## min

<pre>
min(<a href="#min-integers">integers</a>)
</pre>

Returns the minimum of given elements.

**PARAMETERS**


| Name  | Description | Default Value |
| :-------------: | :-------------: | :-------------: |
| integers |  A list of integers. Must not be empty.   |  none |
